config MTK_USB2JTAG_SUPPORT
	bool "Enable serial-wired JTAG Debugging through usb port"
	help
	  After selecting both this option and MTK_USB2JTAG_SUPPORT in LK,
	  users could type fastboot command 'fastboot oem usb2jtag 1' to
	  enter the USB2JTAG debug mode. ('fastboot oem usb2jtag 0' for
	  returning to normal mode).
	  Note: Parallel-wired JTAG Debugging and USB driver
	  would be disabled in USB2JTAG debug mode.
